graph TD
    A[User Request] --> B[Node 1: Draft Email]
    
    subgraph Persistent Checkpointer
    B -->|Saves State| C(Checkpointer DB)
    end
    
    C --> D{Interrupt Flag: interrupt_before='SendEmail'}
    
    D -->|Halts Execution| E[Graph Sleeps]
    
    subgraph Human-in-the-Loop
    E -->|UI Display| F[Human Manager Reviews Draft]
    F -->|Clicks Approve| G[Resume Graph from Checkpoint]
    F -->|Clicks Reject/Edit| H[Inject 'Command' updating State]
    end
    
    H --> G
    G --> I[Node 2: Send Email]
    I --> J[Return Success]
